title: Content Court: Jared Leto
description: Court is back in session baby and this time it's our highest profile defendant yet- actor, musician, and cult leader Jared Leto! Will AB be able to mount a convincing defense? Or can AI Ian deploy sufficient legal judo to flip this case back around on the prosecution. Find out on Content Court: Jared Leto.
